步掌握在一個小時左右，時間太長容易讓狗玩野了，不好教育。還要注意避免讓它接近市民，以防傳染疾病和寄生蟲。"},{"pid":"0c3ee6fe88936ac22df348cbbf7fbad98159e69f","tid":1409032,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:20:34.000Z","msg":"人阿、我要人阿"},{"pid":"4626f464493653e382a9852534259bdd6496349e","tid":1409032,"uid":268070,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:21:48.000Z","msg":"行出黎啦<br />\n唔好再care遊行影響到今個月搵少左幾多錢<br />\n如果一個地方d差佬可以因為政治立場而亂鳩黎<br />\n你搵錢買到既資產,<br />\n都唔會有保障亦唔會run得好<br />\n醒下啦 <br />\n你所持有資產既優劣緊要過你自己份人工呀<br />\n攪返好個社會先 <br />\n慢慢再搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45355bd49024360fd008cc5a784bdd42280d869","tid":1409032,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:21:53.000Z","msg":"見字請幫拖、衣家衣個時間先最需要你哋"},{"pid":"8e0c32df5cdd52bd3502762723ea995a76adf735","tid":1409032,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:22:41.000Z","msg":"全民dm Emma Watson. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/emmawatson?igshid=b5y3xa4gke0u\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Femmawatson%3Figshid%3Db5y3xa4gke0u&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=e6861d1b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/emmawatson?igshid=b5y3xa4gke0u</a><br />\n<br />\nIG傳送門<br />\n<br />\nHello Emma,<br />\n<br />\nWe're writing to express concern over an incident involving the violation of female rights that has just happened in Hong Kong. As you may have noticed, Hong Kongers are currently experiencing police brutality on a daily basis during the process of fighting aginst the extradition bill imposed by the HK government. Earlier just now a female protestor was arrested near a local police station, during which her pants were violently ripped off against her will. The police officers made no attempt to protect her privacy which was unacceptable on any level. Since the beginning of the protests in June not one of our local feminist organizations have stood out for female rights. <br />\n<br />\nWe are in desperate times and sincerely seek your help in raising international concern over this matter as we can foresee more inicidents like this one are going to happen in the near future if nothing is done to stop police brutality. Thanks a lot for your time!<br />\n<br />\nA group of concerned Hong Kongers"},{"pid":"e0f5bd90fac57d297971d10f8fcb657c38917194","tid":1409032,"uid":292737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:24:23.000Z","msg":"今晚直落聽朝！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535525e6eaaa8faae62d167df763ba9e683680f1","tid":1409032,"uid":61191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:29:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaea0d3db7b5a5cfe1619a53443191f8458116db","tid":1409032,"uid":61191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21765e8022a5faa7d32fccc28a03ee17d28bf79a","tid":1409032,"uid":291625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b5329532d918a05ccf2dbe8f693089361940e29","tid":1409032,"uid":283504,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:30:46.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"e33a233804d1d3d6cb0efa7d0c055c67a1515976","tid":1409032,"uid":25866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:31:59.000Z"